{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Copy/paste fades Select one item first and run the action to copy, then several items to apply the same fades 1 selected item -> COPY 2+ selected items -> PASTE\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
{\colortbl;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Replaces REAPER's default track creation behavior with folder-aware logic optimized for asset organization workflows.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 If no track is selected:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab a new folder track is created at the end of the project\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab two child tracks are automatically created beneath it\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab the folder is immediately collapsed\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 If a regular top-level track is selected:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab a new folder track is created below the selected track\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab two child tracks are automatically created beneath it\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab the folder is immediately collapsed\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 If a collapsed folder parent is selected:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab a new folder track is created after the entire folder block\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab two child tracks are automatically created beneath it\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab the folder is immediately collapsed\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 If an expanded folder parent is selected:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab a single child track is created directly inside the folder\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 If a child track is selected:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab a single track is created below the selected track\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 If the selected child track is the last track in its folder:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab a new child track is created within the same folder\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab folder closing information is automatically transferred to preserve the folder structure\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Newly created folder tracks are created in a fully collapsed state.\par}
}

